      // Including all of them prevents extremely hard-to-debug rendering issues when
      // text is copy-pasted from different sources (Word, web, etc.).
      //
      // | Name        | Char | Unicode | Length            | Common Use                              | Frequency    |
      // |-------------|------|---------|-------------------|-----------------------------------------|--------------|
